{"tid":848871,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"屌你老母陳詠謙寫比EASON果兩首新歌真係次次係SPOTIFY聽親都即SKIP","createTime":"2018-10-05T09:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T18:01:34.000Z","uid":171273,"like":59,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"50bcb39a15aad41578968dbe4dbaf2f542798fc8","tid":848871,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T09:00:32.000Z","msg":"我都未撚試過覺得有eason既歌係聽到會skip<br />\n<br />\n就算近年D國語歌唔係好岩聽 咩我們 讓我留在你身邊 覺得麻麻地都唔撚會skip<br />\n<br />\n今年果兩首咩漸漸同可一可再 真係一聽到就SKIP<br />\n<br />\n你填D乜閪呀屌你老母 九唔撚搭八岩音就塞隻字入去 <br />\n<br />\n真係垃撚圾 無料扮四條<br />\n<br />\n縮返入你老母個閪幫陳柏宇填返D垃圾MK情歌啦  乜撚野向夢想出發的忠粉都填撚得出仲以為自己好閪有料"},{"pid":"4c3d402f654d3eb8197e34d188e77e3994f53a3a","tid":848871,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T09:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871ae434d54cc458313dc4f7d952273fbc19e7cd","tid":848871,"uid":82917,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T09:37:18.000Z","msg":"向前是你 引擎是我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得到一晚兩晚三晚四晚溫暖的片刻<br />\n<br />\n屌爆陳詠謙老母填埋哂啲鳩詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06723802b92fdb9f7bcfe353081ac82f19d410b","tid":848871,"uid":212990,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"陳柏宇 <br />\n<br />\n沒有你 我甚麼都不是<br />\n<br />\n作詞：林若寧<br />\n作曲：Cousin Fung<br />\n編曲：Edward Chan・Cousin Fung @ emp<br />\n監製：Edward Chan"},{"pid":"a869b67d471ad8088f9fb2d14fab059d9073d941","tid":848871,"uid":209554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:33:54.000Z","msg":"個人認為佢除左壯舉其他都係垃圾作品"},{"pid":"141b5dcc406ffcedea3f91479713210f7b65fab4","tid":848871,"uid":145138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:54:20.000Z","msg":"愈反愈紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c0e5ea2cd25b44bcb7fbbe1d9